IN-DI-GO

"Relaxation"
 (2004)

Music is known to have properties to facilitate healing.
Valuable help to relieve stress, for relaxation and regeneration, music is an essential tool for healing in the series "Therapy Room", in which the therapist will find the beautiful and harmonious music, created by the world's best composers of this type of music.
"Relaxation" will help you create a haven, a sanctuary where you can relax, unwind and recover, every day.
It is essential to take the time each day to withdraw from the hustle and bustle of our modern environment to feed our mind and body by moments of rest and relaxation. This soothing music, combined with a loving intention towards your own well-being, is the best prescription to cancel the negative effects of stress and fatigue that we feel as a result of our hectic lives.
